tBoot:`2 连接 BOOT 设备`,firmwareUpgradeStepUpgrade:`3 开始升级`,firmwareUpgradeBootConnected:`BOOT 设备已连接，可以开始升级。`,firmwareUpgradeBootDisconnected:`尚未连接 BOOT 设备。进入 BOOT 后请执行第 2 步重新选择设备。`,firmwareUpgradeLoadLocalBin:`加载本地 BIN 文件`,firmwareUpgradeLocalBinInvalid:`请选择 .bin 固件文件。`,keyboardBacklightGrid:`键位颜色网格`,keyboardBacklightGridTip:`网格会按默认键位布局展示当前收到的每键颜色；灰色表示当前尚未收到该键的颜色回报。`,keyboardMapPanel:`键盘 MAP 视图`,keyboardMapPanelTip:`该接口返回了键盘布局结构，下面按键盘形态渲染每个按键的对应数据，原始 JSON 结果仍保留在下方用于比对。`,keyboardMapTotal:`布局键数`,keyboardMapLayer:`层级`,keyboardMapConfiguredCount:`配置条目`,keyboardMapKey:`按键`,keyboardMapType:`类型`,keyboardMapName:`名称`,keyboardMapContent:`内容`,advancedKeyDetail:`详情`,keyboardMapHid:`HID`,keyboardMapValue:`值`,performanceKeyboardMap:`键盘行程配置图`,performanceKeyboardMapTip:`上方展示整张键盘的行程配置，全局摘要用于快速判断公共值，键位图与明细表用于查看每个按键的触发行程、RT、安全区和工作模式。`,axisDetailsKeyboardMap:`键盘轴体分布图`,axisDetailsKeyboardMapTip:`该视图参考驱动里的换轴页，按键盘形态展示每个键当前使用的轴体、型号和最大行程，便于直接对照整板轴体分布。`,axisDetailsBrandFilter:`品牌筛选`,axisDetailsAllBrands:`全部品牌`,axisDetailsBrandCount:`品牌数量`,axisDetailsVisibleCount:`当前显示键数`,axisDetailsFineTuneCount:`可精调键数`,axisDetailsBrand:`品牌`,axisDetailsAxisName:`轴体名称`,axisDetailsModel:`型号`,axisDetailsRange:`最大行程`,axisDetailsCoefficient:`轴体系数`,axisDetailsPreviewLarge:`轴体大图预览`,axisDetailsPreviewIcon:`图标`,axisDetailsPreviewTop:`上件`,axisDetailsPreviewBottom:`底座`,axisDetailsPreview:`轴体动态示意`,axisDetailsPreviewTip:`基于当前轴体最大行程和轴体系数生成的小型示意动画。`,axisDetailsFineTune:`精调支持`,axisDetailsFineTuneYes:`支持`,axisDetailsFineTuneNo:`不支持`,performanceGlobalMode:`RT 全局开关`,performanceNormalPress:`全局触发行程`,performanceGlobalRt:`默认 RT`,performanceGlobalSafeZone:`默认安全区`,performanceGlobalAxis:`公共轴体`,performanceKeyCount:`按键数量`,performanceModeRtOn:`开启`,performanceModeRtOff:`关闭`,performanceRtEnabled:`RT ON`,performanceKey:`按键`,performanceTrigger:`触发位置`,performanceRtDown:`RT 按下`,performanceRtUp:`RT 释放`,performanceSafeTop:`上安全区`,performanceSafeBottom:`下安全区`,performanceWorkingMode:`工作模式`,performanceAxis:`轴体`,logoLightingPreview:`Logo 颜色预览`,logoLi